Package: GeorgeR
Title: Personal Analysis Environment Setup
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("George", "B. Y.", , "g.beknazar@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to set up a standardized
    analysis environment for both R scripts and R Markdown documents.
    It handles chunk options, caching, and data loading.
